title: The Executioner
occurrences: If I'd meet him at the cafe or the cinema I wouldn't say he's a executioner.
But... can't you understand? When the boys find out that I'm the executioner's daughter... - What?
Is it you who wants to be an executioner?
But... here they don't say anywhere that you're an executioner!
It's the visit for the executioner.
...let my father-in-law to come in...! - It's not possible... - This is the real executioner!
Excuse me... is that one the executioner? - Yes.
Your father-in-law...? - Yes, Amadeo, the executioner...!
...then Carmen, since she was the executioner's daughter, it wasn't easy for her either...
Ah...! Then, your father-in-law, when giving up to be an executioner, would lose the flat... - Yes. As it...
Yes! But I can't be an executioner! What I want is to resign...! - But if you resign you'll lose your flat...
And this is Amadeo! The executioner... 40 years on duty... He's just over there...!
...and he'll come inmediately...! - Look, the wife and son of the executioner!
...I can try to speak with the superiors to obtain another executioner.
